tatistics indicate a disadvantage against the Celtics.\n\nGiven these statistics, the Boston Celtics are likely to have a higher chance of winning the game on Wednesday night.\n\n### **Conclusion:**\n\nBased on the recent performance statistics, the Boston Celtics are favored to win the NBA game against the Detroit Pistons on Wednesday night. The Celtics\' strong offense, led by Jayson Tatum, and their recent home winning streak suggest a significant advantage over the Pistons.', '[\"https:\\/\\/www.si.com\\/nba\\/pistons\\/news\\/betting-odds-prediction-for-detroit-pistons-vs-celtics-on-wednesday-12-4-24\",\"https:\\/\\/www.dimers.com\\/news\\/detroit-pistons-vs-boston-celtics-prediction-nba-ac-december-4-2024\",\"https:\\/\\/www.bleachernation.com\\/picks\\/2024\\/12\\/04\\/celtics-vs-pistons-prediction-expert-picks-odds-stats-and-best-bets-wednesday-december-4-2024\\/\",\"https:\\/\\/www.si.com\\/betting\\/pistons-vs-celtics-prediction-odds-best-nba-prop-bets-wednesday-dec-4\",\"https:\\/\\/www.sportsgambler.com\\/betting-tips\\/basketball\\/detroit-pistons-vs-boston-celtics-prediction-bet-builder-tips-odds-2024-12-04\\/\"]'),
