\' ability to cover the spread as underdogs and their recent performances suggest they might be more competitive than the Pacers, who are struggling with their own losing streak.\n\n**Prediction:**\nBased on the analysis, the Nets are predicted to win with a score of 118-111, aligning with the computer projection models mentioned in the sources[1][2]. The Nets\' ability to cover the spread as underdogs and their recent performances make them a more likely candidate to end their losing streak against the Pacers.\n\n**Conclusion:**\nThe Brooklyn Nets, despite their own three-game losing streak, have a slightly better chance of winning due to their recent performances and ability to cover the spread as underdogs. The Pacers\' struggles with their own losing streak and lower ATS coverage rate make the Nets a more likely candidate to break their losing streak.', '[\"https:\\/\\/www.winchestersun.com\\/2024\\/12\\/04\\/pacers-vs-nets-prediction-picks-line-spread-over-under-december-4\\/\",\"https:\\/\\/foxsports1360.iheart.com\\/content\\/2024-12-04-pacers-vs-nets-predictions-odds-stats-december-4\\/\",\"https:\\/\\/www.cbssports.com\\/nba\\/news\\/pacers-vs-nets-odds-line-spread-start-time-2024-nba-picks-december-4-predictions-from-proven-model\\/\",\"https:\\/\\/www.espn.com\\/nba\\/game\\/_\\/gameId\\/401704886\\/pacers-nets\",\"https:\\/\\/www.foxsports.com\\/nba\\/indiana-pacers-vs-brooklyn-nets-dec-04-2024-game-boxscore-42377\"]'),
