challenge without Chet Holmgren. The New York Knicks, with their improved roster, also pose a threat, but their overall health and depth need to be closely monitored.\n\n### **Impact on Team Performance:**\n- **Boston Celtics:** Their strong core and relatively healthy roster make them a consistent threat.\n- **Oklahoma City Thunder:** The absence of Chet Holmgren could impact their defense and overall performance.\n- **Cleveland Cavaliers:** Their early-season success is tempered by a recent cold streak, which could impact their playoff readiness.\n- **New York Knicks:** The addition of key players has improved their chances, but their overall health and depth need to be closely monitored.\n\n### **Conclusion:**\nThe Boston Celtics remain the favorites to win the NBA championship due to their strong core and relatively healthy roster. However, the Oklahoma City Thunder, Cleveland Cavaliers, and New York Knicks are strong contenders, with the Thunder facing a significant challenge without Chet Holmgren and the Knicks needing to maintain their improved roster health.', '[\"https:\\/\\/www.foxsports.com\\/stories\\/nba\\/2024-25-nba-finals-odds-team-futures\",\"https:\\/\\/sports.betmgm.com\\/en\\/blog\\/nba\\/finals-odds-championship-nba-betting-bm05\\/\",\"https:\\/\\/www.espn.com\\/espn\\/betting\\/story\\/_\\/id\\/40379566\\/nba-championship-odds-2024-25-betting-favorites\",\"https:\\/\\/www.usatoday.com\\/story\\/sports\\/nba\\/2024\\/10\\/18\\/nba-2024-25-season-power-rankings-champship-odds\\/75569184007\\/\",\"https:\\/\\/www.sportsbookreview.com\\/picks\\/nba\\/finals-odds\\/\"]');
