ll and Miles Bridges, struggle with a negative net rating and higher points allowed per 100 possessions[2].\n\n### Summary\nBased on the analysis:\n- The Cavaliers are likely to win the game due to their superior team performance, strong defensive metrics, and current winning streak.\n- The projected score from computer models suggests a Cavaliers win with a final tally of 118-108[1].\n\nThis projection aligns with the Cavaliers\' strong overall performance and the Hornets\' struggles this season.', '[\"https:\\/\\/foxsportspgh.iheart.com\\/content\\/2024-12-07-cavaliers-vs-hornets-predictions-odds-stats-december-7\\/\",\"https:\\/\\/3stepsbasket.com\\/nba\\/charts\\/\",\"https:\\/\\/www.coursehero.com\\/file\\/128844164\\/202201-3650module-0docx\\/\",\"https:\\/\\/basketball.realgm.com\\/nba\\/odds\\/91259\\/cavaliers-vs-hornets-nba-match-player-stats-12-7-2024\",\"https:\\/\\/quizlet.com\\/488562453\\/module-2-flash-cards\\/\"]'),
