egic shifts for the Arizona Cardinals from the provided sources.\n\nThis information highlights the potential impact of the Seahawks\' coaching changes but does not provide a comparative analysis with the Cardinals due to the lack of relevant data on the Cardinals\' coaching situation.', '[\"https:\\/\\/www.nfl.com\\/news\\/seahawks-gm-john-schneider-i-don-t-feel-a-step-back-coming-in-2024-with-new-coaching-staff\",\"https:\\/\\/www.seahawks.com\\/news\\/seahawks-announce-seven-additions-to-2024-coaching-staff\",\"https:\\/\\/www.espn.com\\/nfl\\/story\\/_\\/id\\/42605251\\/2024-nfl-coaching-changes-latest-news-rumors-firings-hires\"]'),
