(1894, 'Gather statistics on the Seahawks\' performance in December games over the past five years.', 'Data Gathering Agent', 'Medium', '2024-12-08 21:06:32', 56, 1, 'To gather statistics on the Seattle Seahawks\' performance in December games over the past five years, here are some factual findings based on available data:\n\n## 2019 Season\n- On December 15, 2019, the Seahawks won against the Carolina Panthers with a score of 30-24[2][3].\n- On December 22, 2019, they lost to the Arizona Cardinals with a score of 13-27[2][3].\n- On December 29, 2019, the Seahawks lost to the San Francisco 49ers with a score of 21-26[1][2][3].\n\n## 2020 Season\n- On December 6, 2020, the Seahawks lost to the New York Giants with a score of 12-17.\n- On December 13, 2020, they lost to the New York Jets with a score of 40-3, but then won against the Washington Football Team on December 20, 2020, with a score of 20-15.\n- On December 27, 2020, the Seahawks won against the Los Angeles Rams with a score of 20-9[3].\n\n## 2021 Season\n- On December 5, 2021, the Seahawks lost to the San Francisco 49ers with a score of 30-23.\n- On December 12, 2021, they lost to the Houston Texans with a score of 33-13.\n- On December 26, 2021, the Seahawks lost to the Chicago Bears with a score of 25-24.\n- On January 2, 2022, they won against the Detroit Lions with a score of 51-29, although this is technically in January, it is close to the December period[3].\n\n## 2022 Season\n- On December 4, 2022, the Seahawks lost to the Las Vegas Raiders with a score of 40-34 (in overtime).\n- On December 11, 2022, they won against the Carolina Panthers with a score of 30-24.\n- On December 24, 2022, the Seahawks lost to the Kansas City Chiefs with a score of 24-10[3].\n\n## 2023 Season\n- On December 10, 2023, the Seahawks lost to the San Francisco 49ers with a score of 16-28.\n- On December 18, 2023, they won against the Philadelphia Eagles with a score of 20-17.\n- On December 24, 2023, the Seahawks won again