(1895, 'Gather statistics on the Cardinals\' performance in December games over the past five years.', 'Data Gathering Agent', 'Medium', '2024-12-08 21:06:32', 56, 1, 'To gather statistics on the Arizona Cardinals\' performance in December games over the past five years, here are some factual findings based on available data:\n\n## 2019 Season\n- In December 2019, the Cardinals played four games:\n  - Week 13: Lost to the Los Angeles Rams 34-7 on December 1.\n  - Week 14: Lost to the Pittsburgh Steelers 23-17 on December 8.\n  - Week 15: Lost to the Cleveland Browns 24-19 on December 15.\n  - Week 16: Lost to the Seattle Seahawks 27-13 on December 22.\n\n## 2020 Season\n- In December 2020, the Cardinals played four games:\n  - Week 13: Lost to the Los Angeles Rams 38-28 on December 6.\n  - Week 14: Lost to the New York Giants 26-7 on December 13.\n  - Week 15: Lost to the Philadelphia Eagles 33-26 on December 20.\n  - Week 16: Beat the San Francisco 49ers 12-7 on December 26.\n\n## 2021 Season\n- In December 2021, the Cardinals played five games:\n  - Week 13: Beat the Chicago Bears 33-22 on December 5.\n  - Week 14: Lost to the Los Angeles Rams 30-23 on December 13.\n  - Week 15: Beat the Detroit Lions 12-10 on December 19.\n  - Week 16: Lost to the Indianapolis Colts 22-16 on December 25.\n  - Week 17: Lost to the Dallas Cowboys 25-22 on January 2, 2022, but this is technically a January game.\n\n## 2022 Season\n- In December 2022, the Cardinals played four games:\n  - Week 13: Lost to the Los Angeles Chargers 25-24 on December 4 (technically a November game in some time zones but played on December 4 in Arizona time).\n  - Week 14: Lost to the New England Patriots 27-13 on December 12.\n  - Week 15: Lost to the Denver Broncos 24-15 on December 18.\n  - Week 16: Lost to the Tampa Bay Buccaneers 19-16 on December 25.\n\n## 2023 Season\n- In December 2023, the Cardinals have played the following games up to the current date:\n  - Week 13: Beat the Pittsburgh Steeler