(1899, 'Investigate the home/away performance differential for both teams during the current season.', 'Performance Differential Analysis Agent', 'Medium', '2024-12-08 21:06:32', 56, 1, 'To analyze the home/away performance differential for the Seattle Seahawks and the Arizona Cardinals during the current season, here are the key findings based on the provided sources:\n\n## Seattle Seahawks\n\n- **Home Performance:**\n  - The Seahawks had a four-game home skid before their Week 12 win against the Cardinals. This win was their first at Lumen Field since September 22[1][3][4].\n  - As of Week 12, the Seahawks\' home record was 3-4[3].\n  - Notably, the Seahawks have had strong defensive performances at home, including a 16-6 win over the Cardinals and a 24-3 win over the Miami Dolphins earlier in the season[1][3][4].\n\n- **Away Performance:**\n  - There is no detailed breakdown of their away record in the provided sources, but it is mentioned that the Seahawks have a overall record of 6-5 as of Week 12[1][3].\n\n## Arizona Cardinals\n\n- **Home Performance:**\n  - The Cardinals\' home record as of the latest information is 4-3, but specific details about their home performances are not extensively covered in the provided sources. However, it is noted that they have played a tough schedule with six losses against teams with a combined record of 55-18[5].\n\n- **Away Performance:**\n  - The Cardinals\' away record is 2-3 as of Week 12, following their loss to the Seahawks in Seattle[3][5].\n\n## Summary\n\n- **Seattle Seahawks:**\n  - Home: 3-4, with notable defensive wins at Lumen Field.\n  - Away: No specific record provided, but an overall 6-5 record.\n\n- **Arizona Cardinals:**\n  - Home: 4-3, with tough losses against strong teams.\n  - Away: 2-3, including a recent loss to the Seahawks.\n\nThese findings indicate that both teams have mixed performances at home and away, but the Seahawks have recently shown strong defensive capabilities at home, while the Cardinals face challenges in both settings against strong opponents.', '[\"https:\\/\\/www.si.com\\/nfl\\/seahawks\\/game-day\\/game-recap-seahawks-dominate-cardinals-seize-nfc-west-lead\",\"https:\\/\\/www.espn.com\\/nfl\\/game\\/_\\/gameId\\/401547638\\/seahawks-cardinals\",\"https:\\/\\/www.espn.com\\/nfl\\/game\\/_\\/gameId\\/401671775\\/cardinals-seahawks\",\"https:\\/\\/www.si.com\\/nfl\\/seahawks\\/seahawks-news\\/seahawks-defense-delivers-best-performance-yet-vs-cardinals\",\"https:\\/\\/www.cbssports.com\\/nfl\\/gametracker\\/live\\/NFL_20241208_SEA@ARI\\/\"]');
